  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA19">
<l>aruḷā toḻiyumē yālilaimē laṉṟu</l>
<l>teruḷāta piḷḷaiyāyc cērntā – ṉiruḷāta</l>
<l>cintaiyarāyc cēvaṭikkē cemmalartūyk kaitoḻutu</l>
<l>muntaiyarāy niṟpārkku muṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will he remain without being gracious, he who that day joined</l>
<l>the banyan leaf as an innocent child, – to those who stand before [him]</l>
<l>as the foremost, [folding their] hands in worship [and] strewing red blossoms</l> 
<l>for [his] red feet, being without darkness in [their] minds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
